ziganka-container-store (0.2.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Fix snapclient default SNAPSERVER_HOST to 127.0.0.1 (host networking).
  * Fix music-assistant routing port to 8095 (was incorrectly 1704).
  * Fix homeassistant: set init: false to allow s6-overlay to run as PID 1.
  * Fix homeassistant: remove /etc/localtime bind mount (breaks postinst).
  * Fix snapclient: move Dockerfile into assets/ so it is included in package.
  * Replace SVG icons with 256x256 PNG icons as required by packaging tools.

 -- Stig Dreyer <stig.dreyer@busy-brain.de>  Wed, 07 May 2026 00:00:00 +0200

